snippet.textDisplay: This song has become part of my daily ritual...my day doesn't feel complete without listening to this song at least once. Beautiful conceptually, executed with briliance and so much soul! This song is easily my favorite on Coke Studio India. Kudos to this team and Papon, and of course, Anwesha for her impeccable singing - I get chills with the things that the sarod and table player do along with Anwesha. I could go on, but what's the need? I'll just listen to the song instead =) Thank you for this!
